name: v2.1.1
body:
## What's Changed

* Added **ASN input** support by @ShubhamRasal in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/445
```console
echo AS15133 | naabu
```
* Added **host exclusion** by open **port threshold** by @parrasajad in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/416
```console
echo AS15133 | naabu -pts 100
```
* Added **automatic host discovery** support by @Mzack9999 in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/418
* Added documentation for using [naabu as library](https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu#using-naabu-as-library) by @Mzack9999 in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/446

## New Contributors
* @ShubhamRasal made their first contribution in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/445

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/compare/v2.1.0...v2.1.1

name: v2.0.8
body:
## What's Changed


* Added **Host Discovery** support by @Mzack9999 in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/346
* Added I**Pv6** port scan support by @Mzack9999 in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/328
* Added **IP Version** selection for scan by @parrasajad in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/375
* Added nmap support to passive scan mode by @Ice3man543 in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/335
* Added source port input support with `source-ip` flag by @Mzack9999 in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/345
* Added `health-check` flag support by @Mzack9999 in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/350
* Added support to include cdn information by @LuitelSamikshya in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/324
* Added end-to-end implementation of socks5 proxy authentication support by @mmishalov in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/356
* Added timeout on stdin read by @Mzack9999 in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/373
* Fixed waitgroup panic crash by @parrasajad in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/382
* Fixed race condition crash by @Mzack9999 in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/392
* Fixed panic crash with host discovery fix by @LuitelSamikshya in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/390
* Fixed unnecessary usage of limit by @akkuman in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/389
* Fixed typo in `options.Ports` by @hahwul in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/397
* Fixed error when config dir does not exists by @maggick in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/368
* Fixed cidr error via networkpolicy upgrade by @Mzack9999 in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/333
* Fixed resume issue condition by @Mzack9999 in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/327

Issues closed in release: https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/milestone/4?closed=1

name: v2.0.7
body:
## What's Changed
* **Added passive port enumeration using Shodan [Internetdb API](https://internetdb.shodan.io)** by @Mzack9999 in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/303
```yaml
   -passive               display passive open ports using shodan internetdb api
```
* Added nmap ips grouping by range by @Mzack9999 in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/304
* Fixed bug producing duplicate output in JSON format by @LuitelSamikshya in https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu/pull/314
